					<h2 class="comment-author">
													<a class="comment-author-link" href="http://www.bscichicago.com" itemprop="author">jon guenther</a>
											</h2>
					<time class="comment-meta-item" datetime="2016-06-07T09:57-04:00" itemprop="datePublished"><a href="#comment-8561" itemprop="url">07 June 2016 at 9:57 am</a></time>
														</div>
